"+ \\rho\\, (\\mathbf{u}^{n} \\cdot \\nabla)\\mathbf{u}^{n+1}\n"
"\\;=\\; -\\nabla p^{n+1} + \\mu\\, \\Delta \\mathbf{u}^{n+1},"
msgstr ""
"\\rho\\, \\frac{\\mathbf{u}^{n+1} - \\mathbf{u}^{n}}{\\Delta t}\n"
"+ \\rho\\, (\\mathbf{u}^{n} \\cdot \\nabla)\\mathbf{u}^{n+1}\n"
"\\;=\\; -\\nabla p^{n+1} + \\mu\\, \\Delta \\mathbf{u}^{n+1},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:56
#: f038481ea82e4d978725bfc9ee80476a
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"(convection linearized by lagging the advecting velocity to "
":math:`\\mathbf{u}^n`). The script implements this as a transient variant of"
" the cavity assembler, with the mass term :math:`\\rho/\\Delta t \\cdot u\\,"
" v` added to the diagonal block along with a corresponding SUPG residual:"
msgstr ""
"（对流项通过将输运速度滞后取为 :math:`\\mathbf{u}^n` 来线性化）。脚本将其实现为方腔装配器的瞬态变体，在对角块上加入质量项 "
":math:`\\rho/\\Delta t \\cdot u\\, v` 以及相应的 SUPG 残差："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:62
#: 7abfddae66e64891b5fc7708565f279b
msgid "examples/fluid/cylinder_flow/cylinder_flow.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/fluid/cylinder_flow/cylinder_flow.py（核心部分）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:80
#: 945f59e3b156449dbc969eb5398c3a8d
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The previous-timestep solution :math:`\\mathbf{u}^n` enters the RHS through "
"a separate ``NodeAssembler`` (``MomentumRHSAssembler``) that contributes "
":math:`\\rho/\\Delta t\\, \\mathbf{u}^n \\cdot v`. Both assemblers share the"
" same ``tau`` field, updated each step to reflect the local cell Reynolds "
"number."
msgstr ""
"上一时间步的解 :math:`\\mathbf{u}^n` 通过一个独立的 ``NodeAssembler``\\ （\\ "
"``MomentumRHSAssembler``\\ ）进入右端项，贡献 :math:`\\rho/\\Delta t\\, \\mathbf{u}^n"
" \\cdot v`\\ 。两个装配器共享同一个 ``tau`` 场，每一步都会更新以反映局部网格单元的雷诺数。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:88
#: c0ce35a25f084f72a6c64ad8197798a7
msgid "Stabilization"
msgstr "稳定化"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:90
#: a67f49e46ee4432abc52e197f4631aa7
msgid ""
"The cylinder problem is more demanding than the cavity: upstream cells see "
"nearly-uniform flow, the wake region needs fine-grained convection-dominated"
" stabilization. The script uses an **adaptive** :math:`\\tau`:"
msgstr ""
"圆柱问题比方腔更为苛刻：上游网格单元看到的几乎是均匀流，而尾迹区域则需要精细的对流主导型稳定化。脚本采用一个\\ **自适应**\\ 的 "
":math:`\\tau`\\ ："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:95
#: 6d1ed09ea7e24c548fe9b227a2808e9f
msgid ""
"\\tau \\;=\\;\n"
"\\left[\n"
"  \\left(\\frac{2}{\\Delta t}\\right)^2\n"
"  + \\left(\\frac{2|\\mathbf{u}|}{h}\\right)^2\n"
"  + \\left(\\frac{4\\nu}{h^2}\\right)^2\n"
"\\right]^{-1/2},"
msgstr ""
"\\tau \\;=\\;\n"
"\\left[\n"
"  \\left(\\frac{2}{\\Delta t}\\right)^2\n"
"  + \\left(\\frac{2|\\mathbf{u}|}{h}\\right)^2\n"
"  + \\left(\\frac{4\\nu}{h^2}\\right)^2\n"
"\\right]^{-1/2},"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:104
#: 812dfb97a49a4fce9f36216e151d0bcf
msgid ""
"evaluated per element from the local mesh size :math:`h` and velocity "
"magnitude. This makes the diffusive part of SUPG dominate where the flow is "
"slow and the convective part dominate in the wake."
msgstr ""
"它在每个单元上由局部网格尺寸 :math:`h` 与速度大小计算得到。这使得 SUPG 的扩散部分在流速较慢处占主导，而对流部分在尾迹中占主导。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:111
#: 1c381cb2aa3a4a63b9318f16522198ca
msgid "Post-processing"
msgstr "后处理"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:113
#: ed22b7da2b6649fe86d01932da1b0c10
msgid ""
"At every saved frame the script derives a **vorticity** field :math:`\\omega"
" = \\partial_x v - \\partial_y u` by :math:`L^2` projection: assemble a mass"
" matrix :class:`~tensormesh.MassElementAssembler`, build the projection "
"right-hand side :math:`\\tilde\\omega` from :math:`\\partial_x v - "
"\\partial_y u` (itself assembled with a :class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler`),"
" and solve :math:`M\\,\\omega = \\tilde\\omega`. This is the standard recipe"
" for recovering a smooth nodal field from element-wise gradients on "
"piecewise-linear FEM."
msgstr ""
"在每个保存的帧上，脚本通过 :math:`L^2` 投影导出一个\\ **涡量**\\ 场 :math:`\\omega = \\partial_x v"
" - \\partial_y u`\\ ：装配一个质量矩阵 :class:`~tensormesh.MassElementAssembler`\\ ，由"
" :math:`\\partial_x v - \\partial_y u`\\ （其本身用 "
":class:`~tensormesh.NodeAssembler` 装配）构造投影右端项 :math:`\\tilde\\omega`\\ ，再求解 "
":math:`M\\,\\omega = \\tilde\\omega`\\ 。这是在分片线性有限元上从逐单元梯度恢复光滑节点场的标准做法。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:124
#: b9d10e4c643948f2a6a50be9f4182d64
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The von Kármán street is the qualitative signature to look for: once the "
"wake destabilizes (typically after :math:`t \\gtrsim 5`) vortices shed "
"alternately from the top and bottom of the cylinder at a Strouhal number "
":math:`\\mathrm{St} = f D / \\bar{U} \\approx 0.3`, visible directly in the "
"vorticity animation."
msgstr ""
"冯·卡门涡街是需要关注的定性特征：一旦尾迹失稳（通常在 :math:`t \\gtrsim 5` 之后），涡便以斯特劳哈尔数 "
":math:`\\mathrm{St} = f D / \\bar{U} \\approx 0.3` "
"从圆柱的上下两侧交替脱落，可在涡量动画中直接观察到。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:132
#: 7361293c54fd48a189ef5089efc35f30
msgid "Output and rendering"
msgstr "输出与渲染"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:134
#: cc21726c5f664221af1099cf2a7b3603
msgid ""
"**Frame sequence.** Every ``N`` steps the script renders a three-panel PNG "
"(vorticity, speed, pressure) into ``frames/`` via ``mesh.plot``."
msgstr ""
"**帧序列。**\\ 每隔 ``N`` 步，脚本通过 ``mesh.plot`` 渲染一张三联面板 PNG（涡量、速度、压力）到 ``frames/``"
" 中。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:137
#: 4390dbc6ec5844409249b2412272edff
msgid ""
"**MP4 rendering.** The companion script "
"``examples/fluid/cylinder_flow/render_video.py`` stitches the "
"``frames/*.png`` sequence into ``vortex_street.mp4`` with an ``ffmpeg`` "
"concat pass."
msgstr ""
"**MP4 渲染。**\\ 配套脚本 ``examples/fluid/cylinder_flow/render_video.py`` 通过一次 "
"``ffmpeg`` 拼接将 ``frames/*.png`` 序列合成为 ``vortex_street.mp4``\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:141
#: 415c3c50d9b2485d8340f73e20a3bb1f
msgid ""
"**Final snapshot.** ``cylinder_flow_final.png`` is the same three-panel "
"figure for the last step, for inclusion in talks and reports."
msgstr "**最终快照。**\\ ``cylinder_flow_final.png`` 是最后一步的同款三联面板图，便于用于演讲与报告。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/fluid/cylinder_flow.rst:153
#: b3c502103a2c49daa02fcdc3c41c7480
msgid ""
"*Output of* ``cylinder_flow.py`` *(rendered to MP4 by* ``render_video.py``\\"
" *): the developed von Kármán vortex street behind the cylinder. After an "
"initial symmetric phase, a small asymmetry triggers periodic shedding; "
"vortices alternate sign and convect downstream at roughly the inlet "
"velocity.*"
msgstr ""
"*``cylinder_flow.py`` 的输出（由* ``render_video.py`` *渲染为 "
"MP4）：圆柱后方发展完整的冯·卡门涡街。在初始的对称阶段之后，一个微小的非对称扰动触发周期性脱落；涡的符号交替变化，并以大致等于入口速度的速度向下游输运。*"

